<LegalLayout
  lang="en"
  title="Cookie Policy"
  description="VeloTribe does not use tracking cookies."
  version="1.0.0-draft"
  updated="2026-05-10"
>
  <h2>1. We do not use tracking cookies</h2>
  <p>VeloTribe is built with privacy in mind. This site uses <strong>Cloudflare Web Analytics</strong>, which does not use cookies, fingerprinting, or any other tracking mechanism. No consent banner is required.</p>

  <h2>2. Strictly necessary cookies</h2>
  <p>The site may use technically essential cookies for session continuity and language preference only. These do not require consent under EU law (LSSI-CE Art. 22.2).</p>

  <h2>3. No third-party trackers</h2>
  <p>We do not embed Google Analytics, Meta Pixel, Hotjar, or any social tracking pixel. If we ever add such tools, this policy will be updated and a consent banner will appear before any tracking occurs.</p>

  <h2>4. Browser controls</h2>
  <p>You can configure your browser to reject cookies or notify you when one is set. See your browser documentation.</p>
</LegalLayout>
